title: Dr. Vodder's Manual Lymph Drainage DVD 1 - Basic Body.iso
description:
Dr. Vodder's
Manual Lymph Drainage
DVD 1
Basic Body

The Basic techniques of the original method of Dr. Vodder's Manual Lymph Drainage are shown in this 60 minute (approx.) DVD. Stationary circles, Pump, Scoop, Rotary and Thumb Circle techniques are demonstrated with individual explanations. This is followed by demonstration of the treatment of individual parts of the body, as taught in the Basic course of the Dr. Vodder School. The film is an optimal addition to the practical courses and will make home study easier. It will also serve as a good reminder years later when reviewing the various body part sequences.
